@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container-fluid">
    <h2 class="mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h2>

    <div class="profile-section">
        <p>This Privacy Policy describes how your personal information is collected, used, and shared when you use our Budget Buddy application.</p>

        <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
        <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> This includes your name, email address, username, and any other information you provide during registration or while using the application.</li>
            <li><strong>Financial Information:</strong> When you use Budget Buddy, you may input financial data such as income, expenses, and budget amounts.</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We may collect information about how you use the application, such as the features you access, the time and duration of your usage, and other statistics.</li>
            <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> We may collect information about the device you use to access Budget Buddy, including the device type, operating system, and unique device identifiers.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
        <p>We may use your information for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>To provide and maintain the Budget Buddy application.</li>
            <li>To personalize your experience and provide tailored features.</li>
            <li>To analyze usage patterns and improve the application.</li>
            <li>To communicate with you about updates, support, and other relevant information.</li>
            <li>To ensure the security and integrity of the application.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Sharing Your Information</h3>
        <p>We will not share your personal or financial information with third parties except in the following circumstances:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>With your consent.</li>
            <li>To comply with legal obligations.</li>
            <li>To protect our rights and property.</li>
            <li>With service providers who assist us in operating the application (under strict confidentiality agreements).</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Security</h3>
        <p>We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure.</p>

        <h3>Your Rights</h3>
        <p>You may have certain rights regarding your personal information, including the right to access, correct, or delete your data. Please contact us if you have any requests or questions about your rights.</p>

        <h3>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h3>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the new policy on our website or through other communication channels.</p>

        <h3>Contact Us</h3>
        <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at [Your Contact Email Address].</p>
    </div>
</div>